name: Luminate Online Data Viewer
tagline: A desktop application for Windows and OS X providing realtime reporting for Luminate Online.
body:
### About
The Luminate Online Data Viewer allows organizations to gain insight into the performance of their online marketing campaigns with up-to-the-minute reporting using [Luminate Online Web Services](http://open.convio.com/webservices/).

### Download
The Data Viewer is available as an application for 32- and 64-bit Windows and OS X operating systems.
